20:23.760 --> 20:27.116
We did only have the one cancellation,
you know.

20:27.200 --> 20:29.156
Yeah. Er...

20:30.200 --> 20:33.476
OK, should somebody do something, or...

20:33.560 --> 20:35.471
Like what?

20:35.560 --> 20:36.959
I don't know.

20:38.000 --> 20:39.911
Sing a song?

20:40.000 --> 20:41.956
Or a slow hand-clap.

21:03.720 --> 21:05.551
Hi.

21:05.640 --> 21:08.359
Right. Unless there's anything else?

21:09.480 --> 21:11.391
Oh! Sorry.

21:11.480 --> 21:13.391
Sorry. Did I miss anything?

21:13.480 --> 21:15.436
Oh, sorry about that.

21:15.520 --> 21:17.033
This side?
- Yeah.

21:17.120 --> 21:19.076
And...yes.

21:29.200 --> 21:31.111
Hooray!

21:47.760 --> 21:49.876
Thanks.
- Thank you for coming.

21:49.960 --> 21:52.155
And thank you.
- What for?

21:52.240 --> 21:54.879
For being here. Being you.

21:56.080 --> 21:59.595
I had this fear this morning
that when we were standing up there,

21:59.680 --> 22:02.672
I'd be distracted.
I wanted everything to be so perfect.

22:02.760 --> 22:04.352
And?

22:05.400 --> 22:07.356
And then there was you.

22:08.400 --> 22:11.358
I saw you on David's arm
and the world...stopped.

22:12.400 --> 22:14.356
It was just you and me.

22:15.360 --> 22:17.316
Was that how you felt?

22:18.560 --> 22:21.518
What was all that about with you and David?

22:21.600 --> 22:23.716
Nothing. I'll tell you later.

22:30.520 --> 22:34.274
Pete! We didn't think you would make it.
- Oh, neither did I.

22:34.360 --> 22:37.955
There wasn't a cab to be found.
I finally flagged down a car full of nuns.

22:38.040 --> 22:40.270
You got a lift? I figured you ran.

22:40.360 --> 22:44.478
I did. They dropped me at those
lights there. - What, those lights?

22:44.560 --> 22:45.595
Yeah.

22:45.680 --> 22:48.035
You should think about getting fit.

22:50.200 --> 22:52.077
And smile!

22:55.920 --> 22:57.831
What did he say?

22:57.920 --> 22:59.831
Not now!

22:59.920 --> 23:02.718
Oh, dodging the issue. That's typical!

23:04.320 --> 23:07.630
No, he told me everything. We'll talk later.

23:20.320 --> 23:22.276
Smile.

23:22.360 --> 23:23.839
Keep that off.

23:23.920 --> 23:25.876
Off or on? Make your mind up!

23:27.080 --> 23:29.799
Move in closer together.

23:31.280 --> 23:33.236
A kiss?

23:37.760 --> 23:40.149
Hi. Thanks for coming.
- You look wonderful.

23:40.240 --> 23:42.071
Thank you.

23:43.120 --> 23:45.111
Congratulations, darling.

23:45.200 --> 23:46.713
I'm so happy for you.

23:47.760 --> 23:49.716
Thanks, Mum.

23:51.040 --> 23:54.157
OK, everyone. The reception is at our house.

23:54.240 --> 23:57.357
The address is on the back
of the invitation.

23:57.440 --> 24:00.000
So if you'd make your way over there.

24:02.880 --> 24:04.836
<i>Hey, hey, hey!</i>

24:04.920 --> 24:07.115
Can anyone give me a lift?

24:13.520 --> 24:15.238
