24:19.760 --> 24:21.671
It's gorgeous.

24:21.760 --> 24:24.832
Put your presents there, on the table.
Thanks very much.

24:24.920 --> 24:27.275
There's fruit juice if you're
pacing yourselves,

24:27.360 --> 24:30.318
